sequenceDiagram
  autonumber

  participant U as User (Browser)
  participant SPA as Stitch Web App (SPA)
  participant API as Stitch API
  participant DB as DynamoDB (Tenant + File ACL)
  participant IDP as SSO Directory (Entra ID / Okta)
  participant MAIL as Email (SES)

  Note over U,SPA: User opens Collaborate panel
  U->>SPA: Open Collaborate
  SPA->>API: GET /org/users
  API->>DB: Query users by tenantId
  DB-->>API: Users with account profiles
  API-->>SPA: 200 OK
  SPA-->>U: Render org user list

  SPA->>API: GET /files/{fileId}/acl
  API->>DB: Get file ACL by tenantId + fileId
  DB-->>API: ACL entries
  API-->>SPA: 200 OK

  Note over U,SPA: Invite user with file-level permission
  U->>SPA: Choose user + permission + message
  SPA->>API: POST /files/{fileId}/invites
  API->>DB: Authorize inviter (creator or Owner)
  alt Authorized
    API->>DB: Upsert ACL entry (userId, permission)
    API->>DB: Create invite record (status=Pending)
    API->>MAIL: Send email invite notification
    API-->>SPA: 201 Created
  else Not authorized
    API-->>SPA: 403 Forbidden
  end

  Note over U,SPA: Access enforcement example
  U->>SPA: Click Export
  SPA->>API: POST /files/{fileId}/exports
  API->>DB: Check ACL permission == Collaborator or higher
  alt Allowed
    API-->>SPA: 202 Accepted
  else Denied
    API-->>SPA: 403 Forbidden
  end

